{"artist":null,"title":"Pastrami Bagel Social Club","resource_url":"https://api.discogs.com/releases/5720546","year":"2010","notes":"A wild klezmer/rock fusion by this crazed band of Paris-born punk rockers. Led by the extraordinary young guitarist David Konopnicki, Autoryno hits with a hardedged sound and an exciting musical imagination. Full of youthful energy, massive guitar and centered by a powerful beat, they present eleven instrumentals that combine the power of rock with a taste of Jewish tradition. With Eyal Maoz, Jon Madof, Yoshie Fruchter and a handful of others, David is spearheading a New Jewish Rock Music that has passion, intensity, honesty and a fresh open sound.","uri":"https://www.discogs.com/AutorYno-Pastrami-Bagel-Social-Club/release/5720546","images":[{"uri150":"https://img.discogs.com/TDwihbTMHmwlT8BD4Fuwh_ACYfg=/fit-in/150x150/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(40)/discogs-images/R-5720546-1400846167-7121.jpeg.jpg","height":155,"width":155,"type":"secondary"}],"videos":null,"artists":[{"id":3807621,"name":"AutorYno","role":"","uri":null}],"extraartists":[{"id":3840242,"name":"Loïc Audureau","role":"Accordion","uri":null},{"id":3807620,"name":"Bertrand Delorme","role":"Bass","uri":null},{"id":3840241,"name":"Florent Mery","role":"Clarinet","uri":null},{"id":1602309,"name":"Cyril Grimaud","role":"Drums","uri":null},{"id":3807619,"name":"David Konopnicki","role":"Guitar","uri":null}],"tracklist":[{"extraartists":null,"title":"Ouverture Automatique","position":"1"},{"extraartists":null,"title":"Malossol","position":"2"},{"extraartists":null,"title":"Crapaud","position":"3"},{"extraartists":null,"title":"Kelev","position":"4"},{"extraartists":null,"title":"Traditionnal Hora","position":"5"},{"extraartists":null,"title":"Five Flavours","position":"6"},{"extraartists":null,"title":"Highway To Stertziv","position":"7"},{"extraartists":null,"title":"Les Anges (Otto Theme)","position":"8"}],"series":[{"name":"Radical Jewish Culture"}]}